reviews.content: I worked in health care for 34 years, and this office is typical of so many here in The Villages. The doctor's ads claim to listen to the patient, but this doctor in particular wrote a misdiagnosis in my file , and it was reported to my insurance company, and the doctor was not going to correct it because it would make her look bad, and cause a lawsuit if she were wrong. Now my insurance company won't cover anything because of this wrong diagnosis. Very unhappy.
